properties.script:
out0 = spark.sql(f"""
    SELECT
   '{Config.sourceSystem}' AS SRC_SYS_CD
, TRIM(HISTORYMAINLINE.HISTORYMAINLINEID) as HIST_MNLINE_ID
, TRIM(HISTORYMAINLINE.CONTAINERID) as CNTNR_ID
, TRIM(HISTORYMAINLINE.PRODUCTID) as PROD_ID
, TRIM(HISTORYMAINLINE.RESOURCEID) as RSRS_ID
, TRIM(HISTORYMAINLINE.APPLICATION) as APPL_ID
, TRIM(HISTORYMAINLINE.BASETXNTYPE) as BASE_TXN_TYPE_CD
, TRIM(HISTORYMAINLINE.BATCHID) as BTCH_ID
, CAST(HISTORYMAINLINE.BINNINGINCLUDED as BOOLEAN ) as BINNING_INCLD_IND
, CAST(HISTORYMAINLINE.BONUSINCLUDED as BOOLEAN ) as BNS_INCLD_IND
, TRIM(HISTORYMAINLINE.CALENDARSHIFTID) as CAL_SHFT_ID
, TRIM(HISTORYMAINLINE.CARRIERID) as CARR_ID
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as CCF_EMP_ID
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as CERT_NM
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as CERT_STS_CD
, INT(HISTORYMAINLINE.CHANGECOUNT) as CHG_CNT
, TRIM(HISTORYMAINLINE.CIOMESSAGEID) as CIO_MSG_ID
, TRIM(HISTORYMAINLINE.CIOMESSAGEIDOUTBOUND) as CIO_OUTB_MSG_ID
, TRIM(HISTORYMAINLINE.CLIENT) as CLNT_ID
, TRIM(HISTORYMAINLINE.COMMENTS) as COMT_TXT
, TRIM(HISTORYMAINLINE.COMPOUNDTXNTYPE) as CMPND_TXN_TYPE_CD
, TRIM(HISTORYMAINLINE.COMPUTATIONHISTORYID) as CMPUT_HIST_ID
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as CNTNR_STS_CD
, CAST(HISTORYMAINLINE.DEFECTINCLUDED as BOOLEAN ) as DEFCT_INCLD_IND
, TRIM(HISTORYMAINLINE.DEVICEIDENTIFIERID) as DVC_ID
, TRIM(HISTORYMAINLINE.EMPLOYEEID) as EMP_ID
, TRIM(HISTORYMAINLINE.ESIGREQUIREMENTID) as ESIG_REQ_ID
, TRIM(HISTORYMAINLINE.ETHEXPOSURETYPE) as ETH_EXPSR_TYPE_CD
, case when historymainline.expirationdate = '0000000000' then CAST(NULL AS TIMESTAMP) else to_timestamp(left(historymainline.expirationdate,8),\"yyyyMMdd\") end as EXPN_DTTM
, case when historymainline.expirationdategmt = '0000000000' then CAST(NULL AS TIMESTAMP) else to_timestamp(left(historymainline.expirationdategmt,8),\"yyyyMMdd\") end as EXPN_GMT_DTTM
, TRIM(HISTORYMAINLINE.FACTORYID) as FCTRY_ID
, TRIM(HISTORYMAINLINE.HISTORYID) as HIST_ID
, TRIM(HISTORYMAINLINE.ICONID) as ICON_ID
, CAST(HISTORYMAINLINE.IMPLICIT as BOOLEAN ) as IMPLICIT_IND
, CAST(HISTORYMAINLINE.INREWORK as BOOLEAN ) as IN_RWRK_IND
, CAST(HISTORYMAINLINE.ISFAILED as BOOLEAN ) as IS_FAIL_IND
, CAST(HISTORYMAINLINE.LOCALREWORKINCLUDED as BOOLEAN ) as LCL_RWRK_INCLD_IND
, TRIM(HISTORYMAINLINE.LOGINID) as LGN_ID
, CAST(HISTORYMAINLINE.LOSSINCLUDED as BOOLEAN ) as LOSS_INCLD_IND
, case when historymainline.manufacturingdate = '0000000000' then CAST(NULL AS TIMESTAMP) else to_timestamp(left(historymainline.manufacturingdate,8),\"yyyyMMdd\") end as MFG_DTTM
, case when historymainline.manufacturingdategmt = '0000000000' then CAST(NULL AS TIMESTAMP) else to_timestamp(left(historymainline.manufacturingdategmt,8),\"yyyyMMdd\") end as MFG_GMT_DTTM
, case when historymainline.mfgdate = '0000000000' then CAST(NULL AS TIMESTAMP) else to_timestamp(left(historymainline.mfgdate ,14),\"yyyyMMddHHmmss\")end as MFG_2_DTTM
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as MFG_ORDR_NM
, TRIM(HISTORYMAINLINE.MFGPROCESSOVERRIDESID) as MFG_PRCS_OVRDS_ID
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as NC_REF_ID
, CAST(HISTORYMAINLINE.ETHNCRCREATED as BOOLEAN ) as NCR_CRT_IND
, TRIM(HISTORYMAINLINE.ETHNCRFAILURECODEID) as NCR_FAIL_CD_ID
, TRIM(HISTORYMAINLINE.CDOTYPEID) as OBJ_TYPE_ID
, CAST(HISTORYMAINLINE.ETHOPCOMPLETIONQTY AS DECIMAL(18,4)) as OP_CMPLT_QTY
, TRIM(HISTORYMAINLINE.OPERATIONID) as OPR_ID
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as ORDR_STS_NM
, TRIM(HISTORYMAINLINE.OWNERID) as OWN_ID
, TRIM(HISTORYMAINLINE.PARAMETRICDETAILID) as PARAMETRIC_DTL_ID
, TRIM(HISTORYMAINLINE.PRODUCTIONIDENTIFIER) as PRDTN_ID
, CAST(HISTORYMAINLINE.QUALITYESIGCONFIRMED as BOOLEAN ) as QUAL_ESIG_CNFRM_IND
, CAST(NULL AS INT) as RECON_CNT
, CAST(NULL AS BOOLEAN) as REOPED_IND
, TRIM(HISTORYMAINLINE.RESOURCEAVAILABILITY) as RSRS_AVLBLTY_CD
, TRIM(HISTORYMAINLINE.RESOURCESTATUSCODEID) as RSRS_STS_CD
, TRIM(HISTORYMAINLINE.RESOURCESTATUSREASONID) as RSRS_STS_RSN_ID
, TRIM(HISTORYMAINLINE.REVERSALSTATUS) as RVSL_STS_CD
, TRIM(HISTORYMAINLINE.SERVER) as SERVR_ID
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as SHFT_ID
, TRIM(HISTORYMAINLINE.SHIFTNAME) as SHFT_NM
, TRIM(HISTORYMAINLINE.SPECID) as SPEC_ID
, TRIM(HISTORYMAINLINE.STATUS) as STS_CD
, TRIM(HISTORYMAINLINE.STEPENTRYTXNID) as STEP_ENT_TXN_ID
, INT(HISTORYMAINLINE.STEPPASS) as STEP_PAS_NBR
, case when historymainline.systemdate = '0000000000' then CAST(NULL AS TIMESTAMP) else to_timestamp(left(historymainline.systemdate ,14),\"yyyyMMddHHmmss\")end as SYS_DTTM
, case when historymainline.systemdategmt = '0000000000' then CAST(NULL AS TIMESTAMP) else to_timestamp(left(historymainline.systemdategmt ,14),\"yyyyMMddHHmmss\")end as SYS_GMT_DTTM
, CAST(HISTORYMAINLINE.ETHTOTALAMBIENTEXPTIME AS DECIMAL(18,4)) as TOT_AMBNT_EXPSR_TM
, CAST(HISTORYMAINLINE.ETHTOTALDRYEXPTIME AS DECIMAL(18,4)) as TOT_DRY_EXPSR_TM
, CAST(HISTORYMAINLINE.ETHTOTALLIGHTEXPTIME AS DECIMAL(18,4)) as TOT_LGT_EXPSR_TM
, CAST(HISTORYMAINLINE.ETHTOTALNITROGENEXPTIME AS DECIMAL(18,4)) as TOT_NITROGEN_EXPSR_TM
, CAST(HISTORYMAINLINE.ETHTOTALPOSTEXPTIME AS DECIMAL(18,4)) as TOT_POST_EXPSR_TM
, CAST(HISTORYMAINLINE.ETHTOTALPREEXPTIME AS DECIMAL(18,4)) as TOT_PRE_EXPSR_TM
, case when historymainline.txndate = '0000000000' then CAST(NULL AS TIMESTAMP) else to_timestamp(left(historymainline.txndate ,14),\"yyyyMMddHHmmss\")end as TXN_DTTM
, case when historymainline.txndategmt = '0000000000' then CAST(NULL AS TIMESTAMP) else to_timestamp(left(historymainline.txndategmt ,14),\"yyyyMMddHHmmss\")end as TXN_GMT_DTTM
, TRIM(HISTORYMAINLINE.TXNID) as TXN_ID
, TRIM(HISTORYMAINLINE.TXNTYPE) as TXN_TYPE_CD
, TRIM(HISTORYMAINLINE.UDI) as UNIQ_DVC_ID
, TRIM(HISTORYMAINLINE.USERID) as USRID
, TRIM(HISTORYMAINLINE.WORKFLOWSTEPID) as WRKF_STEP_ID
, TRIM(HISTORYMAINLINE.WORKSTATIONID) as WSTN_ID
FROM  {Config.sourceDatabase}.HISTORYMAINLINE as HISTORYMAINLINE  WHERE HISTORYMAINLINE._deleted_ = 'F'  
 
""")
